<TEXT>
<P>
KNBC, which presents good newscasts in general, is a pleasure to watch. 
</P>
<P>
But may I offer a small suggestion to Kelly Lange? Please, Kelly, update your 
makeup and hairdo. The long, bushy hair is so outdated. You are a very 
attractive lady, but a shorter, neater, smarter hair style would be an immense 
help. And please dump those big, circular, dangling earrings. 
</P>
<P>
This is a personal opinion, of course, but many of my friends have expressed 
the same opinions. 
</P>
<P>
Caitlin Adler, Santa Monica 
