<TEXT>
<P>
I played the sappy music behind Secure Horizon's "Harry" commercial of which 
Lorraine Evans (Viewers' Views, Aug. 19) is so tired. 
</P>
<P>
She should realize that the actor who portrays Harry probably will retire 
comfortably, and I will have my monthly phone bill paid each month by royalties 
we receive when the commercial is running. 
</P>
<P>
So in the interest of commerce and long-distance rates, hang in there, 
Lorraine, and hope for the version when Beth doesn't make it. 
</P>
<P>
Peter Siebert, Santa Ana 
