DAUGHTER MAY NOT SUFFER THE PAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A couple who immigrated here from Haiti found the right words and attitudes 
while raising their daughter. She just became Miss America. If this could 
happen, I have no doubt that Sandy Banks and her husband can find a way in 
which to raise a happy and fulfilled Alyssa. 
</P>
<P>
NETTY TURNER 
</P>
<P>
Riverside 
</P>
