<P>
ROAD CLOSURES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Caltrans plans the following closures on area freeways this week: 
</P>
<P>
One lane of the northbound Pasadena (110) Freeway will be closed Tuesday in 
South Pasadena from Fremont Avenue to Glenarm Street from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
One lane of the westbound San Bernardino (10) Freeway will be closed Wednesday 
in El Monte from West Covina Parkway to the San Gabriel River (605) Freeway 
from 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
One lane of the eastbound Pomona (60) Freeway will be closed Friday in Monterey 
Park from Atlantic Boulevard to Markland Boulevard from 9 a.m. to 2:30 p.m. 
</P>
