Johnstone Inn B&amp;B, 403 W. Colorado Ave., Telluride 81435, (800) 752-1901. 
$65-$110. 
</P>
<P>
Ice House, P.O. Box 2909, Telluride 81435, (800) 544-3436. This is a new 
42-room lodge with balconies and/or wraparound decks. $75-$230. 
</P>
<P>
New Sheridan Hotel, 231 W. Colorado Ave., Telluride 81435, (303) 728-4351. 
$40-$70. (Note: The New Sheridan is expected to close soon for renovation.) 
</P>
<P>
Dahl House B&amp;B, P.O. Box 695, Telluride 81435, (303) 728-4158. $35-$60. 
Condo units: $50-$170. 
</P>
