Pennington's Mountain Village Inn, P.O. Box 2428, Telluride Mountain Village, 
Telluride 81435, (800) 543-1437. $90-$235. 
</P>
<P>
For other accommodations, contact Lodges at Telluride, P.O. Box 2038, Telluride 
81435, (303) 728-6621, or Resort Rentals, 673 W. Pacific St., Telluride 81435, 
(800) 538-7754. 
</P>
<P>
For details on rentals at the new Telluride Mountain Village, write to Mountain 
Village Resort Management Co., P.O. Box 11163, Telluride Mountain Village, 
Telluride 81435, (800) 544-0507. 
</P>
<P>
Other information from the Telluride Chamber Resort Assn., P.O. Box 653, 
Telluride 81435, (303) 728-3041, or Telluride Central Reservations, P.O. Box 
1009, Telluride 81435, (800) 525-3455. 
</P>
<P>
Where to eat: Athenian Senate, 123 S. Spruce St., (303) 728-3018. 
</P>
<P>
Powder House, 226 W. Colorado Ave., 728-3622. 
</P>
<P>
La Marmotte, 150 W. San Juan Ave., 728-6232. 
</P>
<P>
Excelsior Cafe, 200 W. Colorado Ave., 728-4250. 
</P>
<P>
Silverglade, 115 W. Colorado Ave., 728-4943. 
</P>
<P>
Skiing: Telluride has more than 750 acres of skiing terrain, 10 lifts. Jerry 
Hulse 
</P>
