<DOCID> 276862 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 16, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Opinion; Part M; Page 2; Column 1; Opinion Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
