UNITED STATES -- DEFENSE; DEFENSE SPENDING; UNITED STATES -- BUDGET; MILITARY 
SUPPLIES AND EQUIPMENT; MILITARY SHIPS; MILITARY AIRPLANES; MILITARY RESERVES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
