<TEXT>
<P>
I just read that "They Like Mike." His Highness the Junk Bond King. Who are 
they? As near as I can determine, they are the very privileged few, with 
virtually no background in jurisprudence, except perhaps Chief Daryl Gates, who 
while not espousing pardon for Milken, seems to be caught up in that very 
dubious practice of unleashing the "talents" of some of our most devious 
criminals to work with the youth of America, thereby setting some very 
confusing parameters for them to employ when they mature. 
</P>
