criminal in the normal sense of the word." Milken is a genuine criminal beyond 
doubt and should spend the bulk of his life in prison. He is a convicted thief 
who has decimated the entire financial structure of our nation, not by 
brilliant displays of acumen, buy by illegal stealth. 
</P>
