which will have generations of Americans paying taxes to back up the "good 
faith" of the U.S. government. As for his supporters, hardly a deep thinking 
brain among them, merely self-centered fools who demonstrate no ken whatsoever 
of the basic tenets of justice. 
</P>
<P>
ROBERT SCHUSTEFF 
</P>
