<P>
FOR KIDS; 
</P>
<P>
A CHILD'S WORKSHOP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KAY DIEHL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NOT ONLY IS Ages + Stages in Beverly Hills a user-friendly toy store, it is a 
creativity center for children as well. 
</P>
<P>
The clang of cymbals or the laughter of toddlers occasionally drifts out of a 
cozy workshop room in the rear of the store, where classes and events, such as 
music and movement for children 3 months to 3 years old, multimedia art and 
fairy-tale theater are held. Advance sign-up ($10 a class) is required for 
these and other classes. 
</P>
<P>
 Ages + Stages, 8950 W. Olympic Blvd., Beverly Hills; (213) 274-4301. KAY DIEHL 
